== nvim ==

my personal nvim config. it's minimal and independent.

i like setting this up like so:

```
su -c 'git clone https://github.com/toxikuu/nvim /etc/xdg/nvim'
echo 'dofile("/etc/xdg/nvim/init.lua")' | install -vDm644 /dev/stdin ~/.config/nvim/init.lua
echo 'dofile("/etc/xdg/nvim/init.lua")' | su - -c 'install -vDm644 /dev/stdin ~/.config/nvim/init.lua'
```
